Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Long Island life
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bt86
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Aug 1978
Long Island history and the north-south divide. Albert Einstein's wartime stay in a rented cottage there. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less